<style type="text/css">
    #parent {
        nav-down: #finish;
    }
</style>
<body>
    <p><p>First, use directional navigation to navigate the focus to the "START" link below.</p></p>
    <!-- In Opera 11.16, directional navigation may be done using Shift+<arrow key>.
         In the SmartTV emulator, use the keypad in the GUI. -->
    <p>Test passes if navigating down once moves the focus to the "FINISH" link.</p><style>

    </style><div id="parent">
      <p><a href="">ignore</a></p>
      <p><a href="">START</a></p>
      <p><a href="" id="end">FINISH</a></p>
      <p><a href="" id="finish">ignore</a></p>
    </div>

